<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>The Gravity</title>

  <style>
    body {
      background: #428675;
      color: white;
      font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 60px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    h3 {
      color: #e0f2ea;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 720px;
      color: #e8f5f0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    /* 🌊 镜像文字（被拉扯） */
    .distortion {
      position: fixed;
      right: 5%;
      bottom: 5%;
      font-size: 60px;
      opacity: 0.08;
      transform: scaleY(-1);
      filter: blur(1px);
      pointer-events: none;
      white-space: nowrap;

      animation: distort 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes distort {
      0% {
        transform: scaleY(-1) skewX(0deg);
      }
      25% {
        transform: scaleY(-1) skewX(10deg);
      }
      50% {
        transform: scaleY(-1) skewX(-8deg);
      }
      75% {
        transform: scaleY(-1) skewX(6deg);
      }
      100% {
        transform: scaleY(-1) skewX(0deg);
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <h1>The Gravity</h1>
  <h3>Project in Development</h3>

  <p>The gravity in people’s words and actions.</p>

  <p>
    Individuals within a democracy may hold the power to change the world. 
    But how can they carry this power within themselves?
  </p>

  <p>
    How do they face the community around them — how do they lead, and how do they confront failure?
  </p>

  <p>
    Democracy encourages individuals to speak, but also asks them to be responsible for what they bring into the world.
  </p>

  <p>
    If it ends in success, that gravity becomes a force that attracts others.  
    But before that — one must first bet on oneself.
  </p>

